<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Confirmation de commande — Andromeda Paris</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f0ede8;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background:#f0ede8;padding:40px 16px;">
  <tr><td align="center">
    <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:600px;width:100%;">

      <!-- HEADER -->
      <tr>
        <td style="background:#191a2e;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;padding:40px 48px 32px;text-align:center;">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1000/9375/5727/files/logo-blanc-andromeda.png?v=1774981994" alt="Andromeda Paris" height="36" style="display:block;margin:0 auto 24px;">
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td style="border-top:1px solid rgba(200,184,154,0.3);"></td></tr></table>
          <p style="color:#C8B89A;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:20px;font-weight:bold;">Confirmation de commande</p>
          <h1 style="color:#ffffff;font-size:26px;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.3;">
            Merci pour votre commande,<br>
            <span style="font-weight:bold;">{{ customer.first_name }}</span>
          </h1>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);font-size:13px;margin-top:12px;">Commande <span style="color:#C8B89A;">{{ order.name }}</span></p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <!-- BODY -->
      <tr>
        <td style="background:#ffffff;padding:40px 48px;">

          <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:32px;">
            Votre commande a bien été reçue et est en cours de préparation. Vous recevrez un email dès son expédition avec votre numéro de suivi.
          </p>

          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:32px;"><tr><td style="border-top:1px solid #eeebe6;"></td></tr></table>

          <!-- Récapitulatif -->
          <p style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C8B89A;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:20px;">Récapitulatif</p>

          {% for line in order.line_items %}
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
            <tr>
              <td width="72" style="vertical-align:top;">
                {% if line.image %}
                <img src="{{ line.image | img_url: '64x64', crop: 'center' }}" alt="{{ line.title }}" width="64" height="64" style="border-radius:8px;display:block;object-fit:cover;">
                {% else %}
                <div style="width:64px;height:64px;background:#f5f3ef;border-radius:8px;"></div>
                {% endif %}
              </td>
              <td style="padding-left:16px;vertical-align:top;">
                <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:4px;">{{ line.title }}</p>
                {% if line.variant_title != 'Default Title' %}
                <p style="color:#888;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:4px;">{{ line.variant_title }} · Qté : {{ line.quantity }}</p>
                {% else %}
                <p style="color:#888;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:4px;">Qté : {{ line.quantity }}</p>
                {% endif %}
              </td>
              <td style="vertical-align:top;text-align:right;white-space:nowrap;">
                <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;">{{ line.price | money }}</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          {% endfor %}

          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:24px 0;"><tr><td style="border-top:1px solid #eeebe6;"></td></tr></table>

          <!-- Totaux -->
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            <tr><td style="padding-bottom:10px;">
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
                <td style="color:#888;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;">Sous-total</td>
                <td style="color:#191a2e;font-size:13px;text-align:right;">{{ order.subtotal_price | money }}</td>
              </tr></table>
            </td></tr>
            <tr><td style="padding-bottom:10px;">
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
                <td style="color:#888;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;">Livraison</td>
                <td style="color:#191a2e;font-size:13px;text-align:right;">
                  {% if order.shipping_price == 0 %}
                    <span style="color:#2d9e5f;font-weight:bold;">Offerte</span>
                  {% else %}
                    {{ order.shipping_price | money }}
                  {% endif %}
                </td>
              </tr></table>
            </td></tr>
            <tr><td style="padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #eeebe6;">
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
                <td style="color:#191a2e;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:12px;">Total</td>
                <td style="color:#191a2e;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;text-align:right;padding-top:12px;">{{ order.total_price | money }}</td>
              </tr></table>
            </td></tr>
          </table>

          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:32px 0;"><tr><td style="border-top:1px solid #eeebe6;"></td></tr></table>

          <!-- Adresses -->
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            <tr>
              <td width="50%" style="padding-right:16px;vertical-align:top;">
                <p style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C8B89A;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:12px;">Livraison</p>
                <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;line-height:1.8;">{{ shipping_address.name }}</p>
                <p style="color:#888;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;">
                  {{ shipping_address.address1 }}<br>
                  {% if shipping_address.address2 != blank %}{{ shipping_address.address2 }}<br>{% endif %}
                  {{ shipping_address.zip }} {{ shipping_address.city }}<br>
                  {{ shipping_address.country }}
                </p>
              </td>
              <td width="50%" style="padding-left:16px;vertical-align:top;">
                <p style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C8B89A;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:12px;">Paiement</p>
                {% for transaction in order.transactions %}
                {% if transaction.status == 'success' %}
                <p style="color:#888;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;">{{ transaction.payment_details.credit_card_company }} •••• {{ transaction.payment_details.credit_card_last_four_digits }}</p>
                <p style="color:#888;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;margin-top:4px;">{{ transaction.amount | money }} débité</p>
                {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>

          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:32px 0;"><tr><td style="border-top:1px solid #eeebe6;"></td></tr></table>

          <!-- CTA -->
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            <tr><td align="center">
              <a href="{{ order.status_url }}" style="display:inline-block;background:#191a2e;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:14px 36px;border-radius:4px;">
                Suivre ma commande
              </a>
            </td></tr>
          </table>

        </td>
      </tr>

      <!-- BANDE -->
      <tr>
        <td style="background:#f9f7f4;border-left:4px solid #C8B89A;padding:20px 48px;">
          <p style="color:#191a2e;font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;font-weight:300;">
            ✦ &nbsp;Votre masque est fabriqué avec une soie de mûrier Grade 6A, 22 mommes — parmi les 5 % de soie les plus rares au monde. Il est préparé avec soin avant de vous être expédié.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <!-- FOOTER -->
      <tr>
        <td style="background:#191a2e;border-radius:0 0 12px 12px;padding:32px 48px;text-align:center;">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1000/9375/5727/files/logo-blanc-andromeda.png?v=1774981994" alt="Andromeda Paris" height="24" style="display:block;margin:0 auto 20px;opacity:0.5;">
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:1.8;font-weight:300;">
            Andromeda Paris — {{ shop.url }}<br>
            Des questions ? Répondez à cet email, nous sommes là pour vous.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top:16px;">
            <a href="{{ shop.url }}/account" style="color:rgba(200,184,154,0.6);font-size:11px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:1px;">Mon compte</a>
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr><td style="height:40px;"></td></tr>
    </table>
  </td></tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
